data.description: Great home that will need some minor fixes and updates. Fabulous neighborhood steps to major stores, restaurants, automobile servicing centers, Doctor's offices, grocers, banks, schools, and more. This is a rare, huge lot of 92+ x 88+ x 127+ x 128+  which makes it parklike grounds.   Plenty of room for a pool. Refrigerator in kitchen is not part of the sale but the refrigerator in the laundry room conveys with the home sale. With your personal touches, this could be your perfect home. The front pictures do not do the interior or the backyard justice. Lots of very open, flowing space makes this home great for entertaining and it has tons of windows overlooking the incredible back yard and allows the natural light to grace this lovely abode. Great place for family gatherings with an enormous den, living room and dining room. Easy access to the interstate, Veterans, West Metairie. Lots of new development in the area.
